{"quote": "Remember Lots wife", "page_title": "Advice", "page_bio": "Advice (also called exhortation) is a form of relating personal or institutional opinions, belief systems, values, recommendations or guidance about certain situations relayed in some context to another person, group or party often offered as a guide to action and/or conduct. Put a little more simply, an advice message is a recommendation about what might be thought, said, or otherwise done to address a problem, make a decision, or manage a situation.", "page_url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Advice"}